description: Dojo Gelato creates authentic Italian-style ice cream and sorbetto every day at our store.We use fresh ingredients, including growth hormone free milk from Ohio and, whenever possible, produce from local farmers.  We never use any artificial sweeteners or extracts in the creation of our gelati.These great frozen treats, in addition to our delicious espresso beverages, are sure to brighten your day!
name: Dojo Gelato & Espresso Truck
